OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1784107113
OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murdering
OL,4,Centrepreneur in 1989
OL,6,FDetectives have arrested a man on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder as part of
OL,8,Finvestigations into the fatal shooting
OL,9,Fof a Southampton entrepreneur more
OL,10,Fthan 35 years ago.
OL,12,FRichard ''Ricky'' Haywood was shot
OL,13,Fmultiple times in his flat above
OL,14,FAmbiance Jewellers, on Shirley Road,
OL,15,Fon October 16 1989.
OL,17,FUntil now, nobody has ever been
OL,18,Fcharged with the 36-year-old's murder.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
