OL,3,CMan arrested on suspicion of murdering
OL,4,Centrepreneur in 1989
OL,6,FToday, Hampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,7,FPolice said it had arrested a 55-year-
OL,8,Fold man, who remains in custody.
OL,10,FThe force is continuing to appeal for
OL,11,Fanyone with information to come
OL,12,Fforward.
OL,14,F"No matter how small or insignificant
OL,15,Fit may seem, your information could be
OL,16,Fvital," it said in a statement.
